metadata.name: Verified Cultists
metadata.description:
Crosses for eyes, hooded cultists, Ethereum logos and flickery noise textures. I don't get any prizes for originality here, but these cultists do carry with them a genuine enamel cultist pin badge made of actual atoms and molecules! Iron, Black Nickel and Pantone 485 red paint to be more precise. It even has a "1st Edition" embossed metal backstamp and a... deluxe clutch. 0_0 

After purchase please contact Metageist to fill in the form (also linked from Metageist.com homepage) and send your ETH wallet and a postal address. International postage is covered by the mint price.

Do it for the cult_ure.
